{"tid":1895810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底班狗拉痴牆文宣返去可以點","createTime":"2020-02-24T18:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T18:34:00.000Z","uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"831a64073d0b02190dc78cad97617ece9fffa7ca","tid":1895810,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"痴牆又無刑事毀壞<br />\n班狗會點都要你坐48然後罰$1500了事 <br />\n定會有其他罪鋤得入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇手足知可以解答我"},{"pid":"558aa932a79d28ed734875ba713ccee508c01eea","tid":1895810,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"墜樓、浮屍"},{"pid":"2b325b4f633044315fa1746822d2dfacad723075","tid":1895810,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558aa932a79d28ed734875ba713ccee508c01eea","tid":1895810,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"墜樓、浮屍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6d9cb888f57098595f0e8dafa1eff60d87d884","tid":1895810,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"558aa932a79d28ed734875ba713ccee508c01eea","tid":1895810,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"墜樓、浮屍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:34:00.000Z","msg":"所有比人拉左返去既手足都有呢個風險 <br />\n啲個人資料都比狗炒低曬<br />\n但文宣齋痴 無噴牆既當下<br />\n拉左返去啲狗係咪一定有權叫你坐48<br />\n會唔會有位可以落charge?<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前睇過有人講痴牆呢啲算係同隨地吐痰差唔多<br />\n但呢排成日見文宣痴牆會比人直接塔返狗屋<br />\n想知多啲手足們會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}